(Soory, I forgot to add this in my last post.)

Vulois sat watching the battle at the Alliance from the monitor in 
the embassy. He saw Soundwave standing around. He contacted him.

"Soundwave, we need to get Zardus as happy as possible. If you help 
him, he might come to listen. Help in the battle, but don't do so 
much as if to attract alot of attention, and only kill if someone is 
actually trying to kill you. Keep life alive at all costs! Vulois 
out."

Vulois went back to working on the embassy.
